<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>19</hymn_number>
<author>Haydn, Franz Joseph (1732-1809), Newton, John (1725-1807)</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Ya Ubangiji, mun gode
 Don ka sake ta da mu,
 Har ka tara mu gabanka
 Don mu furta yabonmu.
 Cikin dukan duhun dare
 Kana nan tare da mu.
 Ba abin da ya same mu
 Tun da ka ke tsaronmu.</lyrics>
<title>Ya Ubangiji, Mun Gode LW19</title>
</song>